## 🛠️ Essential Commands

### Setup & Validation

```bash
# Check plugin dependencies
/checkdependencies

# Authenticate to Salesforce org
sf org login web --alias [customer-name]

# Set default org
sf config set target-org [customer-name]
```

### Instance Management

```bash
# Create new customer instance
mkdir -p instances/salesforce/[customer-name]/{reports,data}

# Document org details
echo '{"alias":"[customer-name]","type":"sandbox","lastAccessed":"'$(date +%Y-%m-%d)'"}' > instances/salesforce/[customer-name]/STATUS.json
```

### Common Operations

```bash
# Retrieve metadata
sf project retrieve start --manifest package.xml --target-org [customer-name]

# Deploy metadata
sf project deploy start --source-dir force-app --target-org [customer-name]

# Run query
sf data query --query "SELECT Id, Name FROM Account LIMIT 10" --target-org [customer-name]

# Export data
sf data export tree --query "SELECT Id, Name FROM Account" --output-dir instances/salesforce/[customer-name]/data --target-org [customer-name]
```

### Feedback & Reflection

