## 🔐 Security

### Never Commit

- API keys, tokens, or credentials (`.env` files)
- Customer data or PII (`instances/*/data/`)
- Salesforce authentication files (`.sf/`)
- Internal URLs or endpoints

### Required in .gitignore

```gitignore
# Salesforce auth
.sf/

# Customer data
instances/*/data/
instances/*/backups/
instances/*/*.csv
instances/*/*.json
!instances/*/STATUS.json
!instances/*/README.md

# Environment variables
.env
.env.local
```

